# Single-module LoD addon. Loads exactly one Data file: the bundled
# GroupFinder catalog for the Experimental PTR flavor. The core library will
# auto-LoadAddOn this addon on the first :Get miss against GroupFinder.

Data_XPTR\GroupFinder.lua
